'''集體歇斯底里'''（{{lang-en|mass hysteria}}），或稱'''集體發瘋'''、'''群体性心因性疾病'''<ref>{{cite book |title=疫苗安全性事件：沟通应对的管理：卫生部EPI管理人员和健康促进部门指南[Vaccine safety events: managing the communications response: a guide for Ministry of Health EPI Managers and Health Promotion Units] |date=2015 |publisher=马尼拉：世卫组织西太平洋区域办事处 |isbn=978-92-9061-741-9 |url=https://apps.who.int/iris/handle/10665/208260 |accessdate=2021-05-24 |language=zh |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524065201/https://apps.who.int/iris/handle/10665/208260 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|mass psychogenic illness}}），是一個[[社會學|社會學]]及[[心理學|心理學]]術語，用來指因集體性的[[恐慌|恐慌]]、[[錯覺|錯覺]]和无[[原因论|病因]]的疾病症状通過[[謠言|謠言]]等方式迅速傳播的現象。<ref name="Bartholomew 2001">''Little Green Men, Meowing Nuns and Head-Hunting Panics: A Study of Mass Psychogenic Illness and Social Delusion'', Robert E. Bartholomew, 2001, [[麥克法蘭公司|McFarland Publishing]]</ref>醫學上也用來指一人以上無意識的有類似實際症狀的現象。<ref name="bartholomew-wessely">{{cite journal
