常見的集體歇斯底里表現為一群人都相信他們患上了同樣的疾病。<ref name="csicop.org">{{cite journal|last=Bartholomew|first=Robert E.|coauthors=Erich Goode|title=Mass Delusions and Hysterias: Highlights from the Past Millennium|journal=Committee for Skeptical Inquiry|date=2000-03-06|volume=24|issue=3|url=http://www.csicop.org/si/show/mass_delusions_and_hysterias_highlights_from_the_past_millennium|author=|access-date=2013-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021195040/http://www.csicop.org/si/show/mass_delusions_and_hysterias_highlights_from_the_past_millennium|archive-date=2013-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 即群体性心因性疾病或流行性歇斯底里。<ref name="Weir" />

通常集體歇斯底里發生之初只有一個人因壓力而導致患病或[[歇斯底里|歇斯底里]]，<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200504/s1353989.htm Doubts raised over Melbourne airport scare. 27/04/2005. ABC News Online<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329085107/http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200504/s1353989.htm |date=2010-03-29 }}</ref>隨後其他人也表現出類似症狀，典型的症狀有[[噁心|噁心]]、[[肌無力|肌無力]]、[[驚厥|驚厥]]以及[[頭痛|頭痛]]。<ref>[http://www.acsh.org/healthissues/newsID.155/healthissue_detail.asp ACSH > Health Issues ><!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310172004/http://www.acsh.org/healthissues/newsID.155/healthissue_detail.asp |date=2012-03-10 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=【影片】他們不由自主狂舞狂笑、一起發病：歷史上的「集體歇斯底里」時刻|url=https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/39118|accessdate=2019-08-08|date=2016-04-01|last=影音精選轉載|work=The News Lens 關鍵評論網|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808061841/https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/39118|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==病理学==
尽管集体歇斯底里会在人群中的传播，但是其并没有传染源<ref name="Kelly et al.">{{cite book |last1=Kelly |first1=J.R. |last2=Iannone |first2=R.E. |last3=McCarty |first3=M.K. |editor1=von Scheve, Christian |editor2=Salmella, Mikko |title=Collective Emotions |date=2014 |publisher=OUP Oxford |isbn=978-0-19-965918-0 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yHq9AgAAQBAJ&q=%22mass+psychogenic+illness%22 |chapter=The function of shared affect in groups |access-date=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029084251/https://books.google.com/books?id=yHq9AgAAQBAJ&q=%22mass+psychogenic+illness%22 |deadurl=no }}</ref> ，而且与其他集体性[[妄想|妄想]]不同，集体歇斯底里会表现出具体的躯体症状<ref name="Weir">{{cite journal |last=Weir |first=Erica |date=2005 |title=Mass sociogenic illness |journal=Canadian Medical Association Journal |volume=172 |issue=1 |page=36 |doi=10.1503/cmaj.045027 |pmid=15632400 |pmc=543940 }}</ref>。巴拉厄特纳辛格姆（Balaratnasingam<!--印地语->英语->中文，有误请校正-->）和汉卡两位教授称：“目前人类对于集体歇斯底里的了解并不深，关于其病因则几乎没有确定的说法”<ref name="Balaratnasingam & Janca">{{cite journal |last1=Balaratnasingam |first1=Sivasankaran |last2=Janca |first2=Aleksandar |title=Mass hysteria revisited |journal=Current Opinion in Psychiatry |date=March 2006 |volume=19 |issue=2 |pages=171–74 |doi=10.1097/01.yco.0000214343.59872.7a |pmid=16612198 |url=https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/46b1/85f18c2049bcc96b60fc1e7bab75ee00c9ea.pdf |access-date=2018-10-21 |archive-date=2018-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022033730/https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/46b1/85f18c2049bcc96b60fc1e7bab75ee00c9ea.pdf |deadurl=no }}</ref>。 用来识别集体歇斯底里的因素通常包括：<ref name="Weir"/>
*无合理躯体原因的症状。
*症状持续时间短、通常为良性症状。
*症状迅速发作并迅速恢复。
*在隔绝的群体中发生。
*发病群体中至少某部分人过度焦虑。
*症状通过视觉、声音或口头交流传播。
*从老年人或地位较高的人发作，顺着年龄尺度向下传播。
*女性居多。

英国精神病学家西蒙·韦斯利将集体歇斯底里分为两种：{{refn|name=Protean}}
* 集体焦虑型歇斯底里（''Mass anxiety hysteria''）“由急性焦虑症发作而成，主要发生在学龄儿童身上。事先没有紧张感，通过视觉接触迅速扩散”{{refn|name=Wessely 1987}}。
* 集体运动型歇斯底里（''Mass motor hysteria''） “由运动行为的异常发作而成，任何年龄段均会发生。发作者事先存在紧张感，最初的病例可被确认，且扩散逐步进行……爆发时间可能较长”<ref name="Wessely 1987">{{cite journal |last=Wessely |first=Simon |date=1987 |title=Mass hysteria: two syndromes? |url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/1bab57ccfa1d9296db5f2f0cb8e10e2c0de8c1c3 |journal=Psychological Medicine |volume=17 |issue=1 |pages=109–20 |doi=10.1017/s0033291700013027 |pmid=3575566 |access-date=2019-12-07 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029084252/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Mass-hysteria%3A-two-syndromes-Wessely/1bab57ccfa1d9296db5f2f0cb8e10e2c0de8c1c3 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

尽管有时群体歇斯底里的发展遵循西蒙的分类<ref name="Protean">{{cite journal |last1=Bartholomew |first1=Robert |last2=Wessely |first2=Simon |date=2002 |title=Protean nature of mass sociogenic illness |url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/2BDC2262E104B8A33F3DD49773DA0D8B/S0007125000268578a.pdf/protean_nature_of_mass_sociogenic_illness.pdf |journal=The British Journal of Psychiatry |volume=180 |issue=4 |pages=300–306 |doi=10.1192/bjp.180.4.300 |pmid=11925351 |access-date=2018-10-10 |archive-date=2019-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190130211908/https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/2BDC2262E104B8A33F3DD49773DA0D8B/S0007125000268578a.pdf/protean_nature_of_mass_sociogenic_illness.pdf |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Waller">[http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm?volumeID=22&editionID=177&ArticleID=1541] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026094623/http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm?volumeID=22 |date=2014-10-26 }} Waller, John. "Looking Back: Dancing plagues and mass hysteria." ''The Psychologist'' 22(7) (2009): 644–47. Web. 17 Dec. 2009.</ref>，但也有学者提出了不同情况，如尼日利亚迈杜古里大学的阿里·贡贝等人对西蒙的分类提出质疑，并列举了几次可以同时被分为两种情况的群体歇斯底里的爆发<ref name="Ali-Gombe">Ali-Gombe, A. et al. "Mass hysteria: one syndrome or two?" ''British Journal of Psychiatry'' 1997; 170  387–88. Web. 17 Dec. 2009.</ref>。

美国精神医学学会出版的《[[精神疾病診斷與統計手冊#DSM-IV-TR_分類|精神疾病診斷與統計手冊]]》对群体歇斯底里没有具体的诊断，不过仍在描述[[转换障碍|转换障碍]]的文本中指出：“‘瘟疫型歇斯底里’是指‘暴露’于一个共同的诱发因素之后，在一群人中出现共同症状的情况”。

